<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>부서</title>
    {{>layout/header}}
</head>
<body>
{{>layout/sidebar}}
{{>layout/topbar}}

<div class="container">

<h1>(회사명 들어갈곳 인데 태그넣으면 여러개 회사 다뜸/현재는 회사id) 부서현황</h1>

        <table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1">
            <ul>
                <tr>
                    <td>부서명</td>
                    <td>부서기능</td>
                </tr>
                {{#selectListDpt}}
